        {
            "language": "markdown",
            "source": [
                "1. Arithmetic Operators\r\n2. Assignment Operators\r\n3. Comparison Operators\r\n4. Logical Operators\r\n5. Increment/Decrement Operators\r\n6. Ternary Operator\r\n7. typeof Operator\r\n8. String Operators\r\n9. Nullish Coalescing (??)\r\n10. Optional Chaining (?.)\r\n11. Spread (...)\r\n12. Rest (...)\r\n13. Destructuring\r\n14. in\r\n15. new\r\n16. Bitwise\r\n17. instanceof\r\n18. delete\r\n19. void\r\n20. Comma\r\n🥲first complete 1-9 then learn 10-20 \r\n10-20 good to learn later 🥱if have to much dulla learn own"
            ],
